data.description: Welcome to your next dream home - step inside and you'll immediately notice the great attention to detail - spacious living room features abundant natural light and a cozy fireplace - gourmet kitchen is the perfect place to prepare meals for gatherings with its abundant cabinet space, breakfast bar on the center island, and stainless appliances - downstairs, you'll find the primary suite with its spa-like ensuite bath and huge walk-in closet as well as one guest bedroom and full bathroom - upstairs are two additional bedrooms with a shared bathroom between offering convenience for guests and family alike - additionally, is the spacious bonus room that can be used as a 5th bedroom, a game room, or lounge room - brand new carpet in all of the bedrooms - fully fenced backyard is the perfect spot for hosting barbeques, gardening, or just relaxing on the back patio - spacious shed offers a great storage spot - schedule your private tour today and start envisioning all of the possibilities!
